      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEYOND THE SEA (3) went back and couldn't get into the action last week but was good in coming from a wider barrier and filling a minor placing when resuming at Pinjarra at the previous appearance. A nice draw on the front line should ensure a cosy run and she races well third-up so could find the winners' stall. HUNGER STRIKE (4) continued her consistent form when she finished third after working, beaten 3.2 metres at this circuit and distance last week. Draws lower so expect another good showing. CHACO EAGLE (6) didn't do a bad job when fourth from a similar barrier at this circuit and distance last time out. Go well. KURIOUS BOY (1) has trialled well since the last outing and could be a big improver from the ace draw.",
